The font and control-file assets in this directory are collected from:

- FIGlet 2.2.5 distribution
- figlet.org fonts archive (`https://www.figlet.org/fonts/`)
- ftp.figlet.org archive (`ftp://ftp.figlet.org/pub/figlet/fonts/`)
- TOIlet official distribution (`http://caca.zoy.org/wiki/toilet`)
- `cmatsuoka/figlet-fonts` (`https://github.com/cmatsuoka/figlet-fonts.git`)
- [JavE FIGlet fonts](http://www.jave.de/figlet/fonts.html) (historical mirror where
  shipped `*.flf` files were Zip archives; unpacked to plaintext FIGlet fonts here—see
  `fonts/THIRD_PARTY.md` for the file list and notes)

Only fonts with licensing that allows usage and redistribution in this
repository are included.

From the JavE mirror, `Georgia11.flf` and `georgi16.flf` were not imported: they
trace the commercial Georgia typeface and lack the usual in-file JavE permission line.
The full list of fonts added from that mirror is recorded in `fonts/THIRD_PARTY.md`
under “JavE mirror archive (zip-wrapped bundle)”.

