Additional fonts from figlet.org (`avatar.flf`, `doom.flf`, `epic.flf`,
`mirror.flf`, `morse.flf`, `pyramid.flf`, `runyc.flf`, `speed.flf`,
`wavy.flf`) include explicit licensing/permission
notes in the font file headers and are included under those terms.

---

Additional fonts from ftp.figlet.org (`5x7.flf`, `6x9.flf`, `6x10.flf`,
`graceful.flf`) include explicit permissive/public-domain notices in the font
headers and are included under those terms.

